Package: regsplice
Title: Lasso-based Methods to Detect Differential Exon Usage
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Lukas M.", "Weber", email = "lukas.weber@imls.uzh.ch", 
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Methods to rank genes by evidence for differential exon usage, 
  using l1 regularization (lasso) to improve power. As described in the 
  publication: "regsplice: Model selection by l1 regularization improves power 
  to detect differential exon usage".
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
Suggests: glmnet, BiocParallel
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
